articles.title: Uday, cheetah brought from South Africa, dies; 2nd in a month - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Uday was translocated to India from Waterberg Biosphere of South Africa on February 18. | Latest News India
articles.content:
A six-year-old cheetah, named Uday, who was brought to Madhya Pradeshs Kuno National Park along with 11 others from South Africa, died on Sunday.
